===Noun===
{{en-noun|~}}

# {{lb|en|American spelling|countable}} A [[statement]] or [[claim]] of [[questionable]] [[accuracy]], from no known [[reliable]] source, usually spread by [[word of mouth]].
#: ''There's a '''rumor''' going round that he's going to get married.''
# {{lb|en|American spelling|uncountable}} [[information|Information]] or [[misinformation]] of the kind contained in such claims.
#: ''They say he used to be a thief, but that's just '''rumor'''.''

